<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Whisker & Steam Cat Cafe</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="A cozy cat cafe with rescued resident cats, buttery pastries, and slow mornings made for lingering."
  >
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  >
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <header class="hero">
      <nav class="topbar">
        <a class="brand" href="#top">
          <span class="brand-mark">=^.^=</span>
          <span class="brand-text">Whisker &amp; Steam</span>
        </a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
          <a href="#cats">Cats</a>
          <a href="#visit">Visit</a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <section class="hero-grid" id="top">
        <div class="hero-copy reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Neighborhood Cat Cafe</p>
          <h1>Pour-over coffee, sunbeam naps, and adoptable cats.</h1>
          <p class="hero-text">
            Spend an unhurried afternoon with velvet-pawed regulars, flaky cardamom buns,
            and a lounge designed for purring, reading, and staying longer than you planned.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button primary" href="#visit">Book a Lounge Spot</a>
            <a class="button secondary" href="#cats">Meet the Cats</a>
          </div>
          <ul class="hero-notes">
            <li>Open daily from 8am to 8pm</li>
            <li>Quiet hours every weekday from 2pm to 4pm</li>
            <li>Adoption events every Saturday</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-art reveal">
          <div class="art-card art-main">
            <p class="art-label">Today in the lounge</p>
            <h2>Mochi claimed the window hammock before 9:15.</h2>
            <p>Three cats are currently accepting compliments. Two are accepting chin scratches.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="art-card art-small sun-card">
            <span>Sunbeam Index</span>
            <strong>Excellent</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="art-card art-small pastry-card">
            <span>Pastry special</span>
            <strong>Honey Fig Scone</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="section story reveal">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Why People Linger</p>
          <h2>A cafe built around softness.</h2>
          <p class="mission-text">
            To create a welcoming space where people and shelter cats connect, offering high-quality drinks and a safe, comforting environment that supports adoption and spreads joy to both our customers and the cats that we look over, offering comfort to all those who need it.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-grid">
          <article>
            <h3>Rescue-first lounge</h3>
            <p>
              Every resident cat comes through our shelter partners. The lounge is spacious,
              calm, and structured around the cats' comfort first.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h3>Comfort-forward menu</h3>
            <p>
              Expect single-origin espresso, house chai, grilled toasties, and pastries baked
              for rainy mornings and long catch-ups.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h3>Moments worth keeping</h3>
            <p>
              Journaling nooks, warm wood, leafy corners, and enough natural light to make
              every coffee break feel cinematic.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section menu-section" id="menu">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Cafe Favorites</p>
          <h2>Drinks and bites with main-character energy.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-grid">
          <article class="menu-card reveal">
            <span class="menu-type">Signature Drink</span>
            <h3>Maple Cloud Latte</h3>
            <p>Espresso, maple cream, sea salt, and a cinnamon puff finish.</p>
            <strong>$6</strong>
          </article>
          <article class="menu-card reveal">
            <span class="menu-type">House Favorite</span>
            <h3>Lavender Iced Matcha</h3>
            <p>Bright ceremonial matcha softened with floral syrup and oat milk.</p>
            <strong>$6.50</strong>
          </article>
          <article class="menu-card reveal">
            <span class="menu-type">Bakery Case</span>
            <h3>Cardamom Morning Bun</h3>
            <p>Sticky edges, buttery layers, and just enough sugar crunch.</p>
            <strong>$5</strong>
          </article>
          <article class="menu-card reveal">
            <span class="menu-type">Savory Pick</span>
            <h3>Tomato Melt Toastie</h3>
            <p>Sourdough, roasted tomato jam, mozzarella, and basil oil.</p>
            <strong>$9</strong>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section cats-section" id="cats">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Resident Icons</p>
          <h2>Current lounge celebrities.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-grid">
          <article class="cat-card reveal">
            <div class="cat-avatar peach">M</div>
            <h3>Mochi</h3>
            <p>Window hammock supervisor. Will pose beautifully, then ignore you.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="cat-card reveal">
            <div class="cat-avatar gold">P</div>
            <h3>Pesto</h3>
            <p>Professional shoulder-rider with a weakness for hoodie strings.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="cat-card reveal">
            <div class="cat-avatar moss">L</div>
            <h3>Luna</h3>
            <p>Softest purr in the building. Prefers soft voices and sunlit blankets.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section visit-section reveal" id="visit">
        <div class="visit-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">Plan Your Visit</p>
          <h2>Come for coffee. Stay because a cat chose your lap.</h2>
          <p>
            Walk-ins are welcome in the cafe. Lounge sessions are 50 minutes and include a
            complimentary drip coffee or tea.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="visit-card">
          <div>
            <span class="detail-label">Location</span>
            <p>China town, Chicago, IL</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="detail-label">Hours</span>
            <p>Daily, 8:00 AM to 8:00 PM</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="detail-label">Lounge Pass</span>
            <p>$14 per guest, reservations recommended</p>
          </div>
          <a class="button primary full" href="mailto:hello@whiskerandsteam.com">Reserve by Email</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
